 firm consistency, place the ice cream in a freezable serving dish and into the freezer for 15 minutes before serving.","Decorate with chopped pistachios, coconut flakes or chocolate chips.","Top with whipped cream and chocolate or fruit sauce."],"basicInfo":["medium","15m","12h","8 portions"]}